Generate random Disease Ontology (DO) IDs

random_DO.Rd

Generate random Disease Ontology (DO) IDs

random_DO(n)

Arguments

n

Number of DO IDs.

Details

DO.db package should be installed.

Value

A vector of DO IDs.

Examples

# \donttest{
random_DO(100)
